font-size:13.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >Database n&#234;n d&#249;ng PostgreSQL l&#224;m database ch&#237;nh. V&#7899;i h&#7879; th&#7889;ng d&#224;i h&#7841;n, PostgreSQL c&#243; l&#7907;i th&#7871; l&#7899;n &#7903; transaction, r&#224;ng bu&#7897;c d&#7919; li&#7879;u, quan h&#7879; b&#7843;ng, index v&#224; truy v&#7845;n b&#225;o c&#225;o. Khi c&#7847;n l&#432;u d&#7919; li&#7879;u linh ho&#7841;t, PostgreSQL v&#7851;n c&#243; JSONB. MongoDB kh&#244;ng ph&#7843;i l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n &#432;u ti&#234;n cho h&#7879; th&#7889;ng c&#243; nhi&#7873;u quan h&#7879; nghi&#7879;p v&#7909; v&#236; vi&#7879;c &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o t&#237;nh to&#224;n v&#7865;n d&#7919; li&#7879;u s&#7869; kh&#243; h&#417;n. MySQL d&#249;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c, nh&#432;ng PostgreSQL ph&#249; h&#7907;p h&#417;n n&#7871;u sau n&#224;y c&#7847;n b&#225;o c&#225;o d&#7919; li&#7879;u ph&#7913;c t&#7841;p.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
font-size:13.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=26  align=justify  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:6.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
font-size:13.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >ORM c&#243; th&#7875; d&#249;ng Prisma ho&#7863;c TypeORM. Prisma d&#7877; d&#249;ng, type-safe v&#224; ph&#249; h&#7907;p &#273;&#7897;i nh&#7887; &#273;&#7871;n v&#7915;a. TypeORM linh ho&#7841;t h&#417;n trong m&#7897;t s&#7889; m&#244; h&#236;nh enterprise nh&#432;ng c&#243; th&#7875; ph&#7913;c t&#7841;p h&#417;n. V&#7899;i Thi&#234;n &#272;&#7913;c, n&#7871;u ch&#432;a c&#243; y&#234;u c&#7847;u &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t, Prisma v&#7851;n l&#224; l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n h&#7907;p l&#253;.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
font-size:13.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=26  align=justify  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:6.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
font-size:13.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >Authentication v&#224; authorization &#7903; ph&#432;&#417;ng &#225;n n&#224;y c&#7847;n l&#224;m b&#224;i b&#7843;n h&#417;n: RBAC &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911;, ph&#226;n quy&#7873;n theo module, audit log thao t&#225;c, ch&#237;nh s&#225;ch m&#7853;t kh&#7849;u, reset password, qu&#7843;n l&#253; phi&#234;n &#273;&#259;ng nh&#7853;p v&#224; gi&#7899;i h&#7841;n truy c&#7853;p API. Storage n&#234;n d&#249;ng S3-compatible storage ho&#7863;c Cloudinary t&#249;y nhu c&#7847;u. N&#7871;u &#432;u ti&#234;n qu&#7843;n l&#253; &#7843;nh, resize, CDN v&#224; t&#7889;i &#432;u &#7843;nh nhanh th&#236; Cloudinary ti&#7879;n h&#417;n. N&#7871;u c&#7847;n l&#432;u nhi&#7873;u lo&#7841;i file v&#224; ki&#7875;m so&#225;t chi ph&#237; d&#224;i h&#7841;n th&#236; S3-compatible storage ph&#249; h&#7907;p h&#417;n.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
font-size:13.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=26  align=justify  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:6.0000pt;
margin-left:0.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;text-align:justify;
text-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
font-size:13.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >Hosting/deployment &#7903; ph&#432;&#417;ng &#225;n n&#224;y n&#234;n b&#224;i b&#7843;n h&#417;n: frontend v&#224; admin deploy Vercel ho&#7863;c container ri&#234;ng, backend deploy b&#7857;ng Docker tr&#234;n cloud service, database d&#249;ng managed PostgreSQL, c&#243; m&#244;i tr&#432;&#7901;ng staging v&#224; production ri&#234;ng. CI/CD c&#7847;n ch&#7841;y lint, type check, test, build v&#224; migration c&#243; ki&#7875;m so&#225;t. Monitoring c&#7847;n c&#243; log t&#7853;p trung, error tracking, uptime monitoring v&#224; c&#7843;nh b&#225;o khi API ho&#7863;c database c&#243; v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873;.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Times New Roman';mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
font-size:13.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=26  align=justify  style="margin-top:0.0000pt;margin-right:0.0000pt;margin-bottom:6.0000pt;
